pipeline.referenceName: GET Cadmium API Key from Key Vault

sqlReaderQuery.value:
SELECT
    'HarvesterJsonAPI.asp?APIKey=' + '@{variables('APIKey')}' + '&Method=getPresentationsWithPresenters&eID=' + CAST(Event_ID AS VARCHAR) AS PresentationPresenter_Url
FROM 
    admin.Event_Details WHERE IsActive = 1;
